Truffle fries were perfectly crispy on the outside with enough substance on the inside. Would definitely order again.

Sports bar with a lot of TVs and a regular crowd. Service is excellent and prices are good. Very sports-bar-y. You know how, like, a dive bar can be very divey and then a pub can be very pubby? This is very sports-bar-y.

Nice little sports bar that amazingly wasn't crowded on a Saturday afternoon. They accommodated us as we wanted to watch baseball on a big college football day.  Food was good, although the margherita pizza wasn't the best, thanks to the …

Wow! I just kept thinking Wow. I ordered a Tailgate Burger & my husband ordered the house burger. We both agreed that everything about our meal was absolutely delicious. It was the best burger, fries, & beer that we've had in a long time. Thank you for such a good meal! We'll be back for sure!
